measurements.description: Four nicely arranged flowers on one 18-cm inflorescence; sepals and petals slightly ruffled, petals pronounced midrib, pristine white; lip ruffled, closed over column, white, exterior over column purple, throat gold overlaid purple middle, gold veins, light yellow eyes, midlobe overlaid purple centrally, white veins, irregular purple markings on white margin; substance medium; texture matte.
